      • calExtendedPrice

        public void calExtendedPrice()
        Calculates then sets the extended price of the order. That is multiplying quantity by unitPrice.

      • calHandlingCharge

        public void calHandlingCharge()
                       throws MyValidationException
        Calculates then sets the handling charge of the order. That is finding from the list of charges already set, where the order's quantity is equal to or greater than a certain charge. Will at least apply the lowest handling charge possible.
        Throws:
        MyValidationException
